<section id="scopes" class="py-24 bg-white border-b border-slate-100">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-12 gap-12 items-end mb-20">
      <div class="lg:col-span-8">
        <div class="text-emerald-600 text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-[0.4em] mb-4">Conference Overview</div>
        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold text-emerald-950 leading-tight">
          Bridging Innovation and Human Care
        </h2>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
      <div class="space-y-6 text-slate-500 font-medium leading-relaxed text-justify">
        <p>
          We are pleased to invite you to the Healthcare Excellence and Advancements in Life Treatment & Human Medicine
          – International Conference (HEALTHMED-IC), a global forum dedicated to strengthening clinical excellence,
          accelerating medical and technological innovation, and advancing human-centered healthcare.
        </p>
        <p>
          HEALTHMED-IC brings together researchers, clinicians, biomedical engineers, pharmacists, nurses, public health
          professionals, policymakers, and industry innovators to exchange knowledge and develop actionable solutions to
          today’s most pressing health challenges. Through interdisciplinary dialogue, the conference aims to bridge
          scientific discovery with real-world practice, supporting safer care, better outcomes, and more resilient
          health systems.
        </p>
        <p>
          With the theme “Bridging Technology and Humanity: Advancing Global Health Excellence through Innovation and
          Sustainable Medicine”, HEALTHMED-IC highlights the critical intersection of: Medical and clinical sciences,
          Biomedical engineering and medical technologies, Health informatics and AI in medicine, Pharmaceutical
          sciences and clinical pharmacy, Public health, epidemiology, and environmental health, Nursing, midwifery,
          allied health, and mental health.
        </p>
        <p>
          We warmly invite you to participate by submitting your abstracts and full papers, presenting your research,
          and engaging in high-impact discussions. HEALTHMED-IC welcomes both onsite and virtual participation, ensuring
          an inclusive and globally connected academic and professional experience.
        </p>
        <p>
          Together, let us shape the future of healthcare, where innovation advances responsibly, systems become more
          sustainable, and medicine remains grounded in humanity. We look forward to welcoming you to HEALTHMED-IC.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-4 gap-4">
        <div class="col-span-4 bg-slate-300 rounded-xl relative"></div>
        <div class="col-span-2 bg-slate-300 rounded-xl relative"></div>
        <div class="col-span-2 bg-slate-300 rounded-xl relative"></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
